===Noun===
'''Turkologist'''
# A [[scholar]] of the [[languages]], [[history]] and [[cultures]] of [[Turkic]] peoples, inlcuding, for example [[Turkish]], [[Kazakh]], [[Uzbek]], [[Azeri]], Kyrgyz, [[Uyghur]], [[Tuvan]], [[Altai]], [[Shor]], [[Karakalpak]] and any of the other dozens of Turkic peoples.